Once again the jamming devices, placed in orbit by Unicron's minions, stopped this comm message from reaching the Maximals.

shadowess_azogoth <shadowess_azogoth@...> wrote:WolfBlade::

She made it to the 300 mile range outsde the maximal stronghold.  She 
opened her comlink to the maximal base. "Hey all. Sorry I took so 
long. I'm here to help. I'm still two days journey away.  But I'll 
get there soon enough. Oh yeah, name's WolfBlade. I was sent to help. 
WHen I get thre, I'll give you the rest of the message."

She kept running hoping they heard her. She kept up at full speed, 
praying to the matrix she would get here sooner than she said. but as 
far out as she was, she knew she was right the first time.
